{"tid":1067720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荷蘭烏德勒支槍擊增至3死9傷　市長終於公布土耳其槍手身份","createTime":"2019-03-18T17:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T02:53:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e3ae157486bb44b3b54b6b07e50b6adea6a5c4d4","tid":1067720,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T17:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1448359_1_L_20190318224613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1448359_1_L_20190318224613.jpg&h=e6afa4d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荷蘭烏德勒支發生槍擊案，烏德勒支市長在社交網站發布片段，證實增至3人死亡，9人受傷，又公布逃脫槍手的身份，是37歲土耳其男子塔尼什，又指警方繼續循恐襲動機調查，亦不排除有多於一名槍手。<br />\n<br />\n當局提升當地反恐級別至最高，軍警加強在機場及主要建築物的保安。首相呂特召開緊急會議，商討應對方法。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地星期一早上，有槍手在住宅區附近行駛的單層電車上開槍。全市電車服務暫停，大批警員接報到場並拉起封鎖線調查，當局派出醫療直升機運送傷者到醫院，呼籲路面的司機讓路給緊急車輛。"},{"pid":"58fb5737e500f7bbc33adbd772134350b45231ec","tid":1067720,"uid":130695,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T17:19:42.000Z","msg":"幾時有人係尖沙咀呢啲地方玩下"},{"pid":"4ea62550b3a47924d44efe3e902f3654e5aed19d","tid":1067720,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T01:32:41.000Z","msg":"東正教定伊斯蘭教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789ef91f278e0818469ed89564a993fa1550695b","tid":1067720,"uid":243009,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b14cb960857f8ad8206fc03caeae3a070fa4e73","tid":1067720,"uid":171572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58fb5737e500f7bbc33adbd772134350b45231ec","tid":1067720,"uid":130695,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T17:19:42.000Z","msg":"幾時有人係尖沙咀呢啲地方玩下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:23:49.000Z","msg":"香港地鐵無安檢，如果返工時間在車頭東尾有人拎支自動出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"